Title: Fix reload of graphs if page update countdown is stopped
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: multisite
Date: 1631012872
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.1.0b1

If graphs were viewed and the page reload was paused, even if you clicked on
"stop the countdown", the page was reloaded after 60 seconds.

